2.0 Alpha (third release)
This is an alpha build of Editroid 2.0. Check http://ilab.ahemm.org/ for a newer version. Email: snarfblam@gmail.com
Known Problems: -Sometimes selection isn't shown -Password Data Generator does not take doors in item data into consideration -Editing anything while the map generator is going, or creating a map of the entire game, can cause errors which might crash Editroid.
Reporting problems -List steps to reproduce the problem, if possible -If an unhandled exception window appears, copy and paste the detail
